title: La CQ: nuevo ingreso
overview: A new school year starts at Constantino Quijano High School, where a new generation on of students is ready to create unforgettable moments. Sofi, the confident cheerleading captain, has sworn off dating after her breakup with Alan, the football team's star player. But her resolve is tested with the arrival of Quiqueâ€”a charming new student with a bold dream. Quique is determined to conquer his stage fright and pursue acting, hoping to impress the father he's never met, a renowned singer. Through thrilling adventures, friendships, and unexpected twists, the students of La CQ discover that at this high school, the possibilities are as limitless as their imaginations.
